<p> Dear <%= @name %>;</p>
<p>We have received correspondence on a <%= @contact.contact_type %> from <%=@contact.name%> at <%= @contact.email_address%>. </p>
<p>Copies gone to all registered data managers: (<% @ccs.each do |ccs| %><%=ccs%>,<%end%>)</p>
<p>It has been suggested that the first person in the list takes the lead in responding.
<b>Content of report:</b>
<%= @contact.body %>
</p>

<% if @contact.contact_type == 'Data Problem' %>
<p><a href="<%=Rails.application.config.website%>/contacts/<%=@contact._id%>"> You may review the contact on line if you are logged into the system. </a></p>

<% end%>
<p>
<b>Time:</b>
<%= @contact.contact_time.strftime("%H:%M on %F") unless @contact.contact_time.nil? %>
</p>
<p>
<b>Screenshot:</b>
<% if @contact.screenshot_url %>
<%= image_tag @contact.screenshot_url %>
<% else %>
No screenshot attached.
<% end %>
</p>

<p> The FreeREG Team</p>